::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Walking calmly down the hallway, Zardus looks at Feline. He had to admit she 
was attractive, he would have to compliment DevilDuer and Reptilica on their 
retreival job. Zardus and Feline enter the mess hall, Zardus leading her 
toward the main table in the center.

DevilDuer, seated at another table, turns his head, looking at Feline, 
admiration clearly written in his optics.
